---
title: "When Cybersecurity Embraces Blockchain.
"
collection: talks
type: "Talk"
permalink: https://ritchieschool.du.edu/news-events/events-calendar#/?i=2
venue: "Lunch and Learn in University of Denver"
date: 2019-03-08
location: "Denver, CO"
---

Cyberattacks are on the rise and every year there are numerous cyber incidents that result in severe losses. Sensitive data is always at risks when stored in the cyber space. The revolutionary technologies provided by blockchain can be promising to deal with the increasing cyberthreats. This talk will focus on the blockchain applications in cybersecurity, including the important role of how blockchain can help protect data in the decentralized architecture and ensure the integrity of data provenance. Also future research opportunities of the intersection of cybersecurity and blockchain in the ares of cloud computing, IoT and healthcare will be addressed. 
